            "stanza_text": "Si j'en crois Gustave Claudin,\nEt son livre assuré de plaire,\nOù par un flamboiement soudain,\nLe Paris d'autrefois s'éclaire ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "A l'ancien Café de Paris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Où venaient, quittant leurs repaires,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Des gens qui n'étaient pas maris,",
